{
  "stem": "10745.2",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 24.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I don't remember what time, because the killing of the Berezne [INAUDIBLE], and all was done in one day.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Because it was on a Tuesday.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And Tuesday is a holy day for the Jews.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And because we discussed this after in the bushes and all that.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So they said they were coming to take us to be killed.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There's somebody came from-- ran away from Berezne.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they came to run in.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they said, they'll come to you.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Because they're cleaning out the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They'll come to take you back to Berezne, and they'll kill you.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He was telling us that they murder.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I can tell you an incident that I was in ghetto.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] At one time, they took a rabbi.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We had a rabbi.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Rabbi Gadaze was a very famous rabbi around the district.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And everybody had real respect.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They told him to dig a hole.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "He dug a hole very deep enough.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And they buried him alive.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They watched.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "They took their time, and they watched.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And then they dug him up, and they brought him back to life just to see how long can a person last under the ground.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And they showed to the Jews, this is for a rabbi, because you believe in him.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Now, a lot of the Jews who came and told us they were going to kill us, they didn't believe.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "A lot of them went back to Berezne.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Of course, they were killed.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Me and my mother and my brother-- it was in the evening-- we snuck out of there.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And we ran.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "We started running all night long [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] through ditches, through mud.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "We scratched.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "We ripped ourselves apart all night long.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "This I'll never forget.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
